      "court_date": "2009-07-20 9:00 AM",
      "matters": "Petition To Instruct Trustee<br>Off Calendar Jul-20-2009 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: Joel Blackman for the San Francisco Public Guardian. Kurt Huysentruyt for David Strykowski (Petitioner).<br><br>Mr. Blackman stated that he waived defects. The Court stated that the only issue before the Court was the transfer of the interest in the real property held by Guta into the trust. Mr. Blackman stated that the only concern was that the Public Guardian would have to sign a quit claim deed. The Court granted the petition, (signing the order for the same in open court). <br><br>Judge: David L. Ballati. Reporter: Arlene Howell, CSR#2542. Clerk: Rosie Noguera. Bailiff: Deputy R. Harris.<br>",
